Package sudoku

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CellIndexesPair
    The CellIndexesPair class is used to create a (row, col) pair where row and col are ints Contains final variables because the variables are initiated only once
    Main
    This class is the Main Class of the sudoku game.
    SudokuButtons
    The SudokuButtons class contains every button which appears in the Application The types of button includes digit buttons and game buttons
    SudokuGame
    The SudokuGame class creates an instance of the sudokuGridPane and SudokuButtons class.
    SudokuGenerator
    The SudokuGenerator class use the SudokuSolver class to create a full valid Sudoku game Randomly choose a cell and remove the number, then checks using the SudokuSolver class if the sudoku game is still unique
    SudokuGrid
    The sudokuGridPane class creates a 9x9 grid which contains numbers from 1 to 9.
    SudokuChecker
    The SudokuChecker class is used to check the correctness of the selected cell and if the user resolved the sudoku by comparing user values and the solver values
    SudokuSolver
    The SudokuSolver create a full valid sudoku game for an empty table Resolves Sudoku for a table which is not empty
    Utility
    The Utility class is a final class which contains the grid and subgrid size, which are final ints.
